    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, delivering power to the rear wheels via a variable M differential lock. Significant preventative measures have been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing, ensuring the structural and mechanical longevity of the chassis. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear configuration for precise turn-in and lateral stability. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain exhibits exceptional thermal efficiency and linear power delivery across the entire rev range. A robust, driver-focused machine for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
