    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday reliability. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Graphite Metallic, which retains a deep gloss, though it does show a few minor stone chips on the forward hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with standard highway use. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin featuring supple black leather seating with minimal bolster wear and well-preserved carpets. Every electronic component, from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust; it comes with a full service history, including a recent synthetic oil change and a brake system inspection performed last month. The alloy wheels are free of major curb rash and are wrapped in tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. While there are signs of careful use, this is a high-quality, dependable driver that has been treated with consistent care. It is a solid, turn-key example ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 36500.0,
